Package org.thegalactic.dgraph

This package is designed to represent directed graph.

See: Description

    DGraph<N,E>
    DGraph.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDGraph<N,E>
    AbstractDGraph.
    ConcreteDGraph<N,E>
    This class gives a standard representation for a directed graph by sets of successors and predecessors.
    DAGraph<N,E>
    This class extends the representation of a directed graph given by class ConcreteDGraph for directed acyclic graph (DAG).

    DAGraphFactory.

    DGraphFactory.
